{"tid":370840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民捕獲 62歲發哥 冒住十號波 街上見冧樹落車清理","createTime":"2017-08-23T09:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T11:00:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d461e31670f82543b63b4895bab2ce5d1d0d6938","tid":370840,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/171108_d769991610877d156676eb9de7cfa001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F171108_d769991610877d156676eb9de7cfa001.jpg&h=a02733c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/171108_e02efc514d59fc09a14e95c80478b3f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F171108_e02efc514d59fc09a14e95c80478b3f1.jpg&h=06aaac9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/171109_9b80a7a9f0b73788d0d1d4687fa79743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F171109_9b80a7a9f0b73788d0d1d4687fa79743.jpg&h=618397ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十號風球下，唔使返工唔使返學，你會選擇留喺屋企留意風暴消息？抑或約埋幾隻雀友決戰四方城？<br />\n<br />\n今朝颱風「天鴿」襲港，各區錄得嚴重水浸，大樹倒塌報告。強風肆虐下，莫講話身處戶外有危險，即使留喺屋企都唔安全。不過偏偏有人大無畏，喺風雨飄搖嘅時刻，冒住強風大雨，幫手清理路面，移走塌樹，呢個人，就係發哥周潤發。<br />\n<br />\n今日下晝約兩點，有網民喺IG中，就貼上合照，話自己喺十號風球下，喺窩打老道巧遇發哥喺街上幫手鋸樹，網民仲叫發哥小心啲。相中所見，家住窩打老道附近嘅發哥，戴住黑色帽，着住黑色風褸，今次同網民影相，就罕有冇拎電話，反而係由網民拎住電話Selfie。而該網民事後隨即delete合照。<br />\n<br />\n發哥事後回應《蘋果》指自己當時坐車返緊屋企途中。發哥表示：「見到條馬路有冧樹，所以咪落車幫手執走樹枝，等大家可以行到。」發哥指自己剛從加拿大拍完電影《無雙》，現時正留港休息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170823&amp;guid=57117290&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170823%26guid%3D57117290%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=dMw%2FSDUuvxnscJWfGjG4d8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a92c2cfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170823%26guid%3D57117290%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=d74e621a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170823&amp;guid=57117290&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10d4bac328263232f330593717bf7bc67cc7287","tid":370840,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25388a6aa8dcb6b6ede923d67060faadf0c1277d","tid":370840,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b57b4d172d4a14c6e776277b3b21e0793858613","tid":370840,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a58161546017a22b232ad78c4a78763167ae77","tid":370840,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:46:40.000Z","msg":"仲友